{"type": "article", "id": 42104, "title": "你们外国人做饭用点料，还要搞这么多花样｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-06-16T23:18:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2669, "name": "香料"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 33067, "name": "Tough Slate Design"}, {"id": 41535, "name": "Kitchen Ceremony"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 193, "image": "img/article/article_show/201706170031263E6byCesrfj4QIov.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">作为菜肴的点睛之笔，产地多元的香料在包装设计上已经不再局限于对异域风情的强调，我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/36159.html\">招贴画风格香料包装</a>就是一个有趣的例子。针对这些并不是经常使用的调味品，有不少设计师开始以容器为切入点玩出了新的花样。本周的推荐就是这些让你愿意摆在厨房的设计。</p><h3>Spice Palette by Risa Takeuchi</h3><p>还记得第一次下厨时手忙脚乱的场景吗？为了让初学者更轻松地完成料理，现居布鲁克林的日裔设计师 <a href=\"http://www.risatakeuchi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Risa Takeuchi</a> 带来了这款名为 Spice Palette 的香料包装。每款香料被分成六份放在气密的塑料罩内，份量刚好和一汤勺的相当。这样一来，下厨时只要破开凸起的罩子，就可以根据需要撒香料了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003206QieVgwYMFXEZB5dx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003206VTL04uMNs8EgCPJ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003205ZVX7KxAIW1d5iOtD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706170032065hRHK9yoTIjWmaUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Masters of Bakery by Tough Slate Design</h3><p>如果烘培是一出戏剧的话，香料们自然是舞台上性格各异的演员——抱着这个将香料拟人化的想法，乌克兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://toughslatedesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tough Slate Design</a> 不仅将香料罐设计成了 20 世纪初期那些贴有戏剧广告的圆柱，并且根据香料的特色选择了一语双关的经典作品名，将它们的标签制作成色彩斑斓的海报。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003228WeHa4KfXInyo091E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003227MXYrj6K2PvAyTWRk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003227YtwzBDfs5jh381El.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.473333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003227suKw4QxTrZF6CG1D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.343333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003229er7qGw6fXaoD8Zhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.105833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>it’s a HOT IDEA! by Sarah Sia</h3><p>在加拿大平面设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/SarahSia\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sarah Sia</a> 眼中，香料的使用更像是一次灵感爆发。为了契合 hot idea 这一主题，她将四种热辣的香料放进了灯泡当中，连外部的纸盒也模仿了灯泡包装进行设计。除了独立的小盒子之外，还有三角形的礼盒版，灯泡之间则通过配套的垫子隔开——当你想不到加点什么时，不妨试着用它们抽签，或许会尝到一份意外之喜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003247FcAjVtzilErUsmg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003248iwZgWQ6TBE01527G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003247EFW8C9BhrYAcH5xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003247cCdMH20wk9rvR3gt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Around the World by Jung Ah Kim</h3><p>根据香料产地做文章的包装设计并不少见，新西兰设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/jungahdesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jung Ah Kim</a> 带来的 Around the World 香料系列走的是简洁而优雅的路线。整个系列由来自印度、地中海、中东和墨西哥的 20 种香料构成，小盒子上的花纹融合了香料本身的品种以及四个地区文化中特有的图案。同样的设计也出现在了长条的纸盒上，成组摆放时就像是多了一件装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003304hs8gVt0vwymDrWfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003305n5YOMcZNj1ky83W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003305XrpkCwz45xIbHalU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003305OltG6WTu5JgsvEU4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003304UkOjDtrK2yaXowuv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kitchen Ceremony by Nataliya Ponomareva &amp; Pavel Dubov</h3><p>第一眼看到由俄罗斯设计师 Nataliya Ponomareva 和 Pavel Dubov 为香料品牌 <a href=\"http://www.kitchenceremony.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kitchen Ceremony</a> 打造的黑白包装时，你或许会以为它们是装着化妆品的瓶瓶罐罐——基于此，似乎也不难理解为什么这种不太常见的极简风格被他们称作是一种 kitchen fashion。除了抢眼的的视觉效果以外，深色的容器也因为对光线的阻隔能力，可以让香料不容易变质。作为一个主要在当地农庄内手工生产的品牌，黑色也有助于强化所谓的“高级感”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003324bhqTeRJ5Enrf1X0v.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003324J8IER7BOYj6QVTLh.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003325GT9bV3ndhmrwiv1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706170033248itX19JoaZPe2WSn.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003325oaiHOkhx3JNmPg1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Spice Kit by Luna Ikuta</h3><p>洛杉矶设计师 <a href=\"http://www.lunaikuta.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luna Ikuta</a> 带来的这套香料包装很容易让人联想到实验室里的试剂。在摒弃了不必要的标签之后，Ikuta 只在瓶子的正面保留了香料的首字母缩写，配合喷砂玻璃带给人一种天然朴素的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003411bzxX34d2eZk1ISnP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003411REC1FjklnIw4P5xY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170617003411A0t3ozshNqdIReJZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}